      "order": 1,
      "Description": "In this lesson, you will explore how AI-generated recommendations can shape the choices and perceptions of guests in hospitality and service settings. We will look at how bias can find its way into AI systems, often without anyone intending it, and why this matters for the people receiving those suggestions. You will learn to recognise the signs of biased recommendations and understand the potential impact on guest experience and trust. By the end of the lesson, you will feel more confident in questioning and evaluating AI-generated content rather than accepting it at face value. This practical introduction is designed to help beginners build a critical awareness of AI tools and use them more responsibly in their day-to-day work.",
